 The breakaway faction of the ruling All Progressives Congress (APC), Reformed APC said its leadership has not decided on the party to join yet. Speaking with DAILY INDEPENDENT on reports that its leadership is planning to join the Peoples Democratic Party ( PDP), Prince Kassim Afegbua, the National Publicity Secretary said the rAPC will take its time and weigh its option before making the crucial decision. ” We are yet to decide on which party to join. Right now, we are still members of APC. We will weigh our options very well before deciding on the next move,” he says. comments Do you get a good or bad response from your wife after making love? Discover a great natural solution that changed my story and put an end to weak/premature ejaculation, CLICK HERE. 